</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C314653CFFC8FFA1FF0EFBD8ECBC1CD0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB136B7FFC8FFA1FF0EFBD8ECBC1CD0" blockId="12.[151,1437,259,1229]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B97AEAA5FFC8FFA1FF0EFBD8EE661CFD" bold="true" box="[199,315,1133,1157]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Remarks.</emphasis>
This new species is distinguished from its congeners by its characteristic thoracic coloration. Also, it differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C0E4D34FFC8FFA1FEF3FB25ED021CD0" box="[314,607,1168,1192]" class="Insecta" family="Clusiidae" genus="Sobarocephala" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vockerothi">
<emphasis id="B97AEAA5FFC8FFA1FEF3FB25ED021CD0" box="[314,607,1168,1192]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Sobarocephala vockerothi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the characters stated in the key.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C314653CFFC8FFA1FF0EFB00EB011CB4" box="[199,1116,1204,1229]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BB136B7FFC8FFA1FF0EFB00EB011CB4" blockId="12.[151,1437,259,1229]" box="[199,1116,1204,1229]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B97AEAA5FFC8FFA1FF0EFB00EE131CB5" bold="true" box="[199,334,1205,1229]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name refers to the large surstylus (Greek: 
<emphasis id="B97AEAA5FFC8FFA1FC72FB00EB5F1CB4" box="[955,1026,1205,1228]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">megas</emphasis>
+ 
<emphasis id="B97AEAA5FFC8FFA1FBDBFB01EB161CB4" box="[1042,1099,1204,1228]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">stylis</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
